  "detailed_description": "<strong>Necrophoresis</strong> is a co-op horror game for 1-4 players.<br>You and your team will explore a haunted morgue to find its dark secrets.<br>Use what you can find to make your way through the morgue and find your way out.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 1-4 player online co-op<br>Work together with your team to find items, clues and get out together.<br></li><li> Single player<br>For hardcore gamers, you'll do all the investigation yourself, good luck finishing this one...<br></li><li>No two games are the same<br>Stay focused and alert to find your way out each time.</li></ul><br><strong>Help your friends</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669540/extras/e75f9f4bbd7042892857f00791f7240c.avif?t=1714474640\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br><strong>Hide</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669540/extras/d09622411f5623969aa3905e9aecd313.avif?t=1714474640\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br><strong>Run</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669540/extras/1d584225836e6e4c1122109a348b692b.avif?t=1714474640\" width=480 height=268 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Necrophoresis</strong> is a co-op horror game for 1-4 players.<br>You and your team will explore a haunted morgue to find its dark secrets.<br>Use what you can find to make your way through the morgue and find your way out.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 1-4 player online co-op<br>Work together with your team to find items, clues and get out together.<br></li><li> Single player<br>For hardcore gamers, you'll do all the investigation yourself, good luck finishing this one...<br></li><li>No two games are the same<br>Stay focused and alert to find your way out each time.</li></ul><br><strong>Help your friends</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669540/extras/e75f9f4bbd7042892857f00791f7240c.avif?t=1714474640\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br><strong>Hide</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669540/extras/d09622411f5623969aa3905e9aecd313.avif?t=1714474640\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br><strong>Run</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669540/extras/1d584225836e6e4c1122109a348b692b.avif?t=1714474640\" width=480 height=268 /></span>",
